{
  "stem": "10768.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The papers that Leo brought along, we didn't even have time to look what names we have.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They, they were bought in Cracow from a Czechoslovakian consul through a, through his men who works there, which was getting-- you know, was bribed.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "When we came on the train from Katowice to the first border, which was not too far away, it was dark.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "There was no light.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Absolutely no light, because it was still, still like the wartime of, of the blackouts.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we didn't know even what our names were.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we came to the first post, and the Polish-- the Polish guard, the, the guard at the border, took us all in.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they took away a lot of things from Leo.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I think he had a few-- $5 and a tube of, of toothpaste.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I had quite a few of my military, military pictures.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I was frantic.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I was petrified.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But somehow they were looking for smugglers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And they saw that we are not smugglers, so they let us go.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Because of that, they said, go back on the other side.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "They thought that we are some kind of black marketeering.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But at that time, through a, a roundabout way-- I don't even remember if we were in Bratislava first or how we came until we came to Prague, where there was the Jewish committee and the Briha.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Now, it's really the most admirable thing how the Briha was working.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They were registering everybody.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "They were giving us moral support, that they will try to give us papers to go through from one, through the boundaries.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And from Prague, again, we went wherever they send us.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
